            <td> 
              <h3><a href="mailto:patton@mail.temple.edu">Lois Patton</a> <br>
                Director</h3>
              <h5>Responsible for all aspects of Press operation and management.</h5>
              <p><i>I have an Ed.D. from Columbia University's Teachers College 
                in the area of philosophy and the social sciences, an M.S. in 
                adult education from Indiana University, and a B.A. from Maryville 
                College in liberal arts. I have had the good fortune of working 
                at four university presses and believe in the future and importance 
                of the book, the power of the written word, and the joy of publishing 
                ground-breaking, issue-engaged manuscripts for academic as well 
                as trade markets and audiences.</i> 
              <p>Email: <a href="mailto:patton@mail.temple.edu">patton@mail.temple.edu</a> 
              <hr>
              <h3><a href="mailto:robertss@mail.temple.edu">Shamell M. Roberts</a> 
                <br>
                Rights and Permissions Administrator / Assistant to the Director</h3>
              <h5>Manages rights and permissions at the Press; acts as administrative 
                assistant to the Director.</h5>
              <p><i>I currently reside in Philadelphia. In April 2000, I re-joined 
                the Press staff as a Customer Service Representative, and in January 
                2001 moved to my current position. I graduated from Temple University 
                with a B.A. in Communication, Broadcasting Telecommunication, 
                and Mass Media, and hope to begin working on my master's degree 
                this Fall. During my free time, I enjoy attending church, spending 
                time with my family and friends, reading, listening to music, 
                and surfing the web. I try to do as much as possible at any given 
                time.</i> 
              <p>Email: <a href="mailto:robertss@mail.temple.edu">robertss@mail.temple.edu</a> 
